channel.title: Moparscape, can't connect
channel.description:
Well, i have a mac. the whole entire moparscape webclient loaded, so it got to that page with the 2 cars facing eachother. then i clicked "enter". this was the information:
Username: Zezima Passwrd: 234121234894 IP: 127.0.0.1
then it said something like "could not connect, please click start server and try again". i did that and tried again. it didn't work.... then i reloaded my browser and went to the webserver. i got this:
[img]http://img102.imageshack.us/img102/1/picture5sz0.png[/img]
How do i fix both of those problems?

ok for the first problem you cant connect make sure your server or someone elses server is online and that you have connected to their hamachi if they have it available, make sure you have the correct port it should then work.

for the second problem close the browser and open it again by clicking on the internet explorer symbol and typing in the url again. works for me. hope i helped.
